Package: bbinsightsR
Title: NCAA Feferee and Momentum Insights
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Dallin", "Wilson", , "mayaziggy@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helper functions and visualizations for analyzing NCAA 
    basketball play-by-play data. Extends the functionality of the 'ncaahoopR' 
    package to explore in-game trends, referee behavior, free throw patterns, 
    and team momentum using ESPN-sourced data.
